          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Maintaining Commitment on the Korean Peninsula Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Office of the Director of National Intelligence to report on: (1) the anticipated diplomatic, military, and intelligence impact of a significant reduction or complete withdrawal of U.S. forces from the Republic of Korea; or (2) the significant reduction or permanent suspension of U.S. exercises on or around the Korean peninsula.<br /><b /></p>]]></text>
